ire a larger or more capable craft, especially in the Mid Rim and Outer Rim Territories.','bayonetcc.jpg',NULL,'Source text CC-BY-SA 3.0 from http://d6holocron.com/wiki/Bayonet-class%20Cruiser','["http://d6holocron.com/wiki/Bayonet-class%20Cruiser"]',5771,32572);
