 stabilization while landing and deploying troops.','cc9600.jpg',NULL,'Source text CC-BY-SA 3.0 from http://d6holocron.com/wiki/CC-9600%20Frigate','["http://d6holocron.com/wiki/CC-9600%20Frigate"]',5686,32669);
